Day 2 - Strings programs


1. WAP to reverse string using two pointer.
2. WAP to check Palindrome using two pointer.
3. WAP to print the count of vowels and consonants from given strings.
4. WAP to count occurrence of elements in the given string.
5. WAP to count occurrence of substring in the given string
6. WAP to remove the spaces from the given string
7. WAP to find the duplicate characters from the string
8. WAP to find the largest word from the given string
9. WAP to check whether the given strings are anagram or not.
10. WAP to check whether the given strings are panagram or not.
11. WAP to print first non-repeating character in a string. 


